NAME
    onboardctl

DESCRIPTION
    Toggle visibility of onboard keyboard. Provide optional parameter (-s,-h)
    to specify show/hide toggle action. No parameters will default to toggle.

    This function has [1] optional parameter(s)
        @1 = visibility toggle (hide/show)

SYNOPSIS
    onboardctl [show|hide]

EXAMPLES
    onboardctl --help
    onboardctl --show
    onboardctl --hide

AVAILABLE OPTIONS:
    --help            [show man docs/script help]
    -h, --hide, hide  [hide onboard]
    -s, --show, show  [show onboard]
